{"tid":1101714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"半導體大廠ASML重要商業機密遭中國籍員工竊走","createTime":"2019-04-11T08:24:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T12:35:43.000Z","uid":72009,"like":240,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"197769cc22a8b0d425b4989b50cfa60600543c4a","tid":1101714,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:24:53.000Z","msg":"荷蘭半導體大廠ASML今天傳出重要商業機密遭竊，導致該公司損失上億歐元，而竊取機密的是該公司的中國籍高層員工。<br />\n <br />\n荷蘭財經媒體《金融日報》（Financieele Dagblad）今日報導指出，根據調查，ASML研發部門的中國籍員工將該公司重要機密外洩給中國政府。ASML損失金額高達數億歐元，不過ASML目前尚未找到有力證據顯示此事與中國政府有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190411/1548822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190411%2F1548822&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=bde18e3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190411%2F1548822&h=22b8487d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190411/1548822</a><br />\n<br />\n其實好多鬼佬娶了件中國肉便器都高危 , 應炒晒"},{"pid":"d65d5f6291743c7522cebc08c47e43b91351b11a","tid":1101714,"uid":28765,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T08:40:52.000Z","msg":"財金報章FD引述美國加州上級法院去年一份文件報道，涉事中國籍員工為研發部門高層。多年來，他們進入ASML位於美國聖何塞的內部網絡，盜取源代碼、軟件和定價策略等資料，再轉交有中國政府資金背景的科技公司XTAL。 <br />\n<br />\n報道指，憑竊取回來的技術，XTAL成功從ASML手上搶走南韓三星電子等客戶。加州上級法院去年裁定，XTAL需向ASML賠償2.23億美元，一個月後XTAL申請破產。荷蘭情報部門近年發表的報告，均指中國對國內科技公司帶來威脅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190411/mobile/bkn-20190411160036827-0411_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190411%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190411160036827-0411_00912_001.html&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=699ce36b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190411/mobile/bkn-20190411160036827-0411_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n已經搞掂左"},{"pid":"b09fa76da62be60f840decc251d10a89e0247626","tid":1101714,"uid":60057,"like":110,"dislike":0,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"歐美左膠咗咁多年，終於要還啦，一日迫唔到班傻仔認清自己同緊個咩國家做對手，一日只會繼續沉淪落去"},{"pid":"2ec9f0edf2879e698b08841993b3c8e96a9456d4","tid":1101714,"uid":39552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27bae62fd653b60081cd953914c7ac1030ccb2b1","tid":1101714,"uid":60057,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"b09fa76da62be60f840decc251d10a89e0247626","tid":1101714,"uid":60057,"like":110,"dislike":0,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"歐美左膠咗咁多年，終於要還啦，一日迫唔到班傻仔認清自己同緊個咩國家做對手，一日只會繼續沉淪落去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"唔種族歧視，到時咪有苦自己知囉。<br />\n<br />\n成個國家全體人民都係間諜，你諗住請個美籍歐籍就諗住無事，諗下好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee717ff98fe663282494d6cb0cec2303bf37470","tid":1101714,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c3dfd2e7991b8bd8b4052c56164776c11bcfaf","tid":1101714,"uid":175479,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:42:55.000Z","msg":"冇咁易架，啲歐美內部左膠會掉轉話冇證據做乜要屈人...."},{"pid":"1533e63f6e7d904a51a2dff4256cd736ade3a23f","tid":1101714,"uid":11962,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:43:52.000Z","msg":"支那人無一個係無辜"},{"pid":"c3254df5cc46b3af21239e0b33896d004fbf8568","tid":1101714,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4c3dfd2e7991b8bd8b4052c56164776c11bcfaf","tid":1101714,"uid":175479,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:42:55.000Z","msg":"冇咁易架，啲歐美內部左膠會掉轉話冇證據做乜要屈人...."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T09:44:21.000Z","msg":"歐豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\"